# src Agent Guide

<!-- agent-skill:operational:start -->
## Local Scope

- Own files under `src/`.
- Read the sibling `CLAUDE.md` when present, then root `CLAUDE.md` and root `AGENTS.md`.
- Prefer commands scoped to this folder when supported.
- Keep generated output, caches, and build artifacts out of commits.
- Follow the task ledger, handoff, pathspec commit, and reviewer-gate rules from the root guidance files.

## Validation

- Run the narrowest relevant test first.
- Escalate to the root verification command before completion.
- Cite bulky logs or screenshots by file path or context-mode handle instead of pasting raw output.
<!-- agent-skill:operational:end -->
